start.label: home is where you hang your hat

examples.en: He was filled with nostalgia for his college days.
He remained nostalgic about his days as a young actor.
A wave of nostalgia swept over me when I saw my childhood home.
Tim spoke nostalgically of his first visit to Peru.
Those nostalgic vibes are fading fast.
...the nostalgic allure of America's Wild West still attracts vacationers to ghost towns...
